| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0539 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 004b6175-e3d3-5df4-a310-a5c50a3cfea1"
